dc_title_s: California Department of Fish and Game Region Boundaries: Russian River Basin, 1999
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile shows the California Deptartment of Fish and Game region boundaries within the Russian River basin. These data were derived from a 1999 CDFG region boundaries layer of 1:100000 scale county boundaries.This layer can be used for land management analysis and planning in the Russian River region of California.
